S.FORM: Gaga kska Kska Hunac Meycow ka Panama, 9 00 N, 80 00 W ka gaga na nniqan. Kana ka knlbangan na o 75,420 sq km(hangan na o Tg118) (knlbanga dxgal o 74,340 sq km, knlbangan qsiya o 1,080 sq km). Kana ka sejiqun o niqan 3,705,246 hiyi. Gaga Panama City ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 3 idas 11 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. Manu ka dxgal Panama ga wada sugan 30.50 ka dxgal qpahan, 43.60 ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 25.90 na. Bukung klwaan ta sayang o kiya ka Juan Carlos Varela, pnaah hngkawas2014 idas 7 jiyax 1pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
